<p>Kourtney's outing comes after she was seen arriving for dinner at Nobu Malibu with her ex Scott Disick on Friday last week.</p>

<p>She shares Mason, 10, Penelope, eight, and Reign, five with Scott, who she split from in 2015 after nine years together. </p>

<p>The pair were seen pulling into the eatery together, with the Flip It Like Disick star, 37, risking a run-in with his ex Sofia Richie, who was also dining at the eatery with pals.</p>

